        }}>{`)`}</span>{`
  `}<span parentName="code" {...{
          "className": "text-code-white"
        }}>{`}`}</span>{`
`}<span parentName="code" {...{
          "className": "text-code-white"
        }}>{`}`}</span>{`
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`Setter functions are optional in computed properties. When no setter function is defined, it's treated as a normal stored, read-only property.`}</p>
    <h3>{`Summary`}</h3>
    <ul>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Reference type instance points to the memory address, not the data`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Value type instance points to the data but not the memory address`}</li>
